            <title>[SUREFIRE-1534] Surefire 2.21.0 ClassNotFoundException: org.apache.maven.plugin.surefire.StartupReportConfiguration using reuseForks set to false</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-1534</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
